  "title": "Expectation of Conflict Stimuli ",
  "description": "This dataset contains neuroimaging data from a study investigating the neural mechanisms of expectation and conflict processing. The research examines how the brain anticipates and responds to conflicting stimuli, with implications for understanding cognitive control and decision-making processes. Data were collected from multiple participants and are formatted according to BIDS standards.",
